<HEADLINE>
THE MAN WHO SAVED THE NBA 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact the Los Angeles office
(Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(duplication notice: also sent with `s' code)  
 (EDS: Boldface word in 2nd graf should be italicized.)  
 By CHARLES PAIKERT   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Much has been made of the National Basketball Association's
post-Michael Jordan blues, epitomized by financially troubled
