<P>
   BKN-HAWKS-IZZO _ When he went to bed Friday night, Tom Izzo
believed he was going to become the next coach of the Atlanta
Hawks. But when he awoke Saturday morning he said he could not
leave Michigan State. (Denberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
