<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-13 20:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4358 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p BC-POL-TICKER0514-COX     05-13 0870
